---
title: Crispy Sweet Dijon Tofu with Wild Rice and Glazed Veggies
description: Brown sugar and Dijon mustard are the stars of this dish! Together, they add pops of sweet Dijon flavour to tofu topped with golden, crispy panko and our veggie medley.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-croustillant-a-la-moutarde-de-dijon-sucree-98b5b4da.jpg
